Mickey Katz https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mickey_Katz 0 Mickey Katz (June 15, 1909 – April 30, 1985) was an American comedian and musician who specialized in Jewish humor. He was the father of actor Joel Grey and grandfather of actress Jennifer Grey. Mickey_Katz ( June_15_,_1909 – April_30_,_1985 ) was an_American_comedian and musician who specialized in Jewish_humor .
